Oldham 
said in a statement: 'Oldham Athletic Football Club has been made aware 
of the incident and allegation surrounding one of its players, Cristian 
Montano. The club will commence an immediate internal investigation to 
establish all the relevant facts of the case.

'The
club is co-operating with other agencies in this matter and cannot 
comment on specific facts at this stage. The club will not be issuing 
